    Approach to Our Programs.
    <p>4NTENT provides our users with wellness and empowerment education to allow our users to set intentions while making a difference in the community. 4NTENT’s team is typically made up of mental health professionals, personal trainers, and nutritionists/dietitians. These professionals will be collaborating on your individual wellness profile and across programs to ensure you are getting the support of unique wellness backgrounds. Several wellness models may be used in our approach with our health mentors. Know that you may be asked to engage in specific activities within the programs and you may be asked to complete homework outside of scheduled programs. You are welcome to engage in all of some of our options within your wellness profile. When engaging in any of your programs, you are in the driver’s seat. Please share what you are comfortable with sharing and we may coach you to share additional aspects with other members. All users will be asked to maintain confidentiality of other users when interacting on the site. 4NTENT’s health mentors work as a team and may need to consult with other health mentors regarding your wellness profile.</p>
    <p>Conversations regarding your wellness, goals, and needs will only be disclosed to other 4NTENT health mentors as it pertains to your intentions and will be discussed with you prior to disclosure.</p>
